title: Girl in the Secret Service (1951 Crime Thriller) Woman ... on a Man-hunt

sources.title: Girl in the Secret Service (1951 Crime Thriller) Woman ... on a Man-hunt
sources.description:
Fingerprints don't lie - which is why a state governor with a hidden criminal past wants a file card with his prints stolen from FBI headquarters.  Shirley Wayne stumbles onto the Govenor's secret putting Agents Glen Stedman and Jeff Donley on the case. With Blake and Carl Stockton scheming in the shadows, it’s a race of wits, badges, and double-crosses, and a wild helicopter-motorboat chase, it’s a race to see who outsmarts who before the truth gets buried.

Directed by William A. Berke

Main cast:
Audrey Totter - Shirley Wayne
Cesar Romero - Agent Glen Stedman
George Brent - Agent Jeff Donley
Tom Drake - Carl Chercourt
Raymond Burr - Blake
Raymond Greenleaf - Governor Owen Grisby
